name: DogTinder
prompt:
Create a website for DogTinder, a platform that connects dog owners with interesting dogs nearby. The color scheme should be minimalistic and modern, featuring shades of pink and white. The design style should be clean and user-friendly, with a focus on simplicity and ease of navigation.

The layout should include a header with the DogTinder logo and navigation menu, followed by a hero section with an image of a dog and a call to action button. Below this, there should be a search bar for users to input their location and interests. The main content area should display a grid of featured dogs, each with a photo, name, age, breed, and a brief description. Each dog profile should have a "View Profile" button that leads to more detailed information about the dog.

The footer should contain links to social media platforms, contact information, and legal disclaimers. The overall design should be responsive, ensuring that it looks good on all devices, from desktop computers to mobile phones.
